rows.label: qst300105_msg001
rows.name: Whew, looks like that's the last of 'em.

rows.label: qst300105_msg002
rows.name:
Thanks for that, you really
are lifesavers!

rows.label: qst300105_msg003
rows.name:
I guess we'll have to store these
rations carefully to make sure the
smell doesn't get out...

rows.label: qst300105_msg004
rows.name:
At any rate, you're starting to
shape up into a proper leader!

rows.label: qst300105_msg005
rows.name:
I reckon you'll be able to handle
managing more mercenary missions.

rows.label: qst300105_msg006
rows.name:
Keep up the good work, for old
Vandham's sake if nothing else!
